{"tid":527090,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲迪積克：我值7500萬鎊！","createTime":"2018-01-12T09:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T07:33:49.000Z","uid":333,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5009ee27abda26252fc5dfbf1e0b7ea45b98fac7","tid":527090,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:54:15.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=ZLlp%2BqdNaSGF4Tu9lAAn4S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=85877a9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】利物浦後衛華基爾雲迪積克堅稱，其7500萬鎊的身價是他努力的回報，這身價不會令他感到緊張。<br />\n<br />\n華基爾雲迪積克（Virgil van Dijk）在周日大戰曼城前接受《天空體育》訪問時說，「這不會令我感到緊張，這是我一直以來努力所得到的回報，所以利物浦願意用這個高價羅致我，我不能改變甚麼。」除了利物浦外，車路士和曼城過去一年都對他感興趣，被問到為何選了紅軍，雲迪積克說，「球會的規模、球迷、球員和領隊，這裡的一切都很吸引。」<br />\n<br />\n雲迪積克於今年元旦日以7500萬鎊由修咸頓轉投利物浦，打破後衛轉會紀錄，雖然成為最昂貴後衛，不過雲迪積克認為這個價錢不會影響到他。英足盃對愛華頓的默西賽德打吡是他的地標戰，該役他即用一個絕殺球證明自己的身價。<br />\n<br />\n雲迪積克補充，「你可以見到每次主場比賽氣氛都是一流，我很高興能為這間球會效力。」"},{"pid":"84436a48009dfcb80e8baa2024287b7eb2a95cfb","tid":527090,"uid":158933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:59:36.000Z","msg":"一派膠就一定比人bin c<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce423b8976a52b665574db60daaa342c9ad55dd3","tid":527090,"uid":31151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T10:02:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一派膠就一定比人bin c<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到時又會有笑話po 一場推一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d32cba4d0ae4c0834eaeb3d56b460a03af556fb","tid":527090,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T10:08:40.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"9e